            <li><strong>Development:</strong> We bring your design to life using modern technologies like HTML5, CSS3, and JavaScript.</li>
            <li><strong>Testing:</strong> We test the website on various devices and browsers to ensure it's fully responsive and functional.</li>
            <li><strong>Launch:</strong> We help you launch the website and provide ongoing support to ensure it runs smoothly.</li>
        </ul>

